examples.text: Nagdala ang iya utod sang isa ka sipi nga saging para may makaon man sia nga prutas.

definitions.definition: to slice away a smaller piece of a bigger object by using a sharp tool

examples.text: Naga-utod sia buhok.
examples.translation: He is cutting hair.

examples.text: Ginautod niya ang iya buhok kon tag-ilinit na.
examples.translation: She cuts her hair during summer.

examples.text: Nag-utod sila sang kahoy para sa bag-o nga payag.
examples.translation: They cut trees for the new hut.

examples.text: Gin-utod niya ang pisi.
examples.translation: He cut the rope.

examples.text: Sia na lang mautod sa buhok sang iya nga bana.
examples.translation: She will cut her husband's hair.

examples.text: Utudon niya buhok sang iya bata karon.
examples.translation: He will cut his child's hair later.

examples.text: Utod na ang iya isa ka tudlo.
examples.translation: One of his fingers has been cut.

examples.text: Nagautog ang iya nga kinatawo kon aga.
examples.translation: His penis gets erect in the morning.

examples.text: Ginkadlawan nila kay nag-utog ang kinatawo sang ido.
examples.translation: They were laughing at the dog's erect penis.

examples.text: Mautog na ang imo nga kinatawo pagbugtaw mo sa aga.
examples.translation: Your penis will get erect when you wake up in the morning.

examples.text: Makautog sang kinatawo ang paglantaw sang binastos.
examples.translation: Watching pornography can make your penis erect.

examples.text: Kitaon ang utog sang iya kinatawo
examples.translation: His erection is visible.

examples.text: Palayo kay nagautot ko subong.
examples.translation: Go away because I am farting.

examples.text: Nag-utot sia sa salakyan.
examples.translation: He farted in the car.

examples.text: Mautot ko karon kon wala na tawo.
examples.translation: I will fart later when there are no people around.

examples.text: Sige sia utot tungod kay damo nga kamote iya nakaon.
examples.translation: She kept on farting because she ate a lot of sweet potatoes.

definitions.definition: dogs, other animals to make a long, loud crying sound

examples.text: Nagauwang ang ido kon alas-dos sang kaagahon.
examples.translation: The dog howls every two in the morning.

examples.text: Nag-uwang ang ido kagahapon sang gab-i.
examples.translation: The dog howled yesterday evening.

examples.text: Mauwang ang ila ido kon maglakat sia.
examples.translation: Their dog will howl whenever she leaves.

examples.text: Baskog ang uwang sang ido.
examples.translation: The dog's howl was loud.

examples.text: Hambal nia nga makadto sia.
examples.translation: She said she will come.

definitions.definition: to keep something in place using one's own hands;

examples.text: Hugot ang iya uyat sa kamot sang iya bata.
examples.translation: Her hold on her child's arm is tight.

examples.text: Naga-uyat sila sa sanga sang puno sang mangga.
examples.translation: They are holding onto the branches of the mango tree.

examples.text: Ginhugasan sang iloy ang kamot sang bata kay nag-uyat ini sang duta.
examples.translation: The mother washed her son's hands because he held dirt.

examples.text: Mauyat ka gid dapat sa higot samtang gasakay sa karabaw.
examples.translation: You will have to hold on to the rope while riding the carabao

examples.text: Uyatan niya buas ang bandera sa parada
examples.translation: She will hold the banner at the parade tomorrow.

examples.text: Ginauyatan ni Maria ang kamot sang iya utod para indi ini makulbaan.
examples.translation: Maria is holding her sibling's hand so he will not feel nervous.

examples.text: Nanghugas sia sang kamot kay nauyatan niya ang basurahan.
examples.translation: She washed her hands because she held the trash can.

examples.text: Gin-uyatan sang bata ang higot sang iya ido para indi ini magdalagan.
examples.translation: The child held on to his dog's leash so it will not run.

examples.text: Ginayab-ukan na lang na ang imo nga bestida.
examples.translation: Your dress is gathering dust.

examples.text: Ginyab-ukan ila nga TV.
examples.translation: Their TV gathered dust.

examples.text: Ginaputos niya iya bayo para indi mayab-ukan.
examples.translation: She covers her clothes so it will not gather dust.

examples.text: Nanghatsi sia tungod kay kadamol na sang yab-ok sa ila balay.
